On the Point of Sale Product Searchbar
After typing a product number into the searchbar
Press F6 to quickly add it as a lost sale

If you dont already know the other shortcuts, here they are:
F1 - Invoice  ||  F2 - Quotation  ||  F3 - Refund
F4 - End Document  ||  F5 - Select Customer
